<!-- VISION -->
<section class="vision-section">
  <div class="vision-left">
    <div class="vision-eyebrow">Our Vision</div>
    <blockquote class="vision-quote">To build the #1 student and alumni support system among private liberal arts colleges in the country.</blockquote>
  </div>
  <div class="vision-body">
    <p>The Black Alumni Association of Denison University was formed in 1975 to ensure that alumni remain connected to Denison and to one another long after graduation. Over time, the BAA has evolved from a reunion-centered alumni group into a structured, mission-driven organization.</p>
    <p>We focus on strengthening student success, expanding access to mentorship and career opportunities, growing the value of the alumni network, and contributing to the development of peer alumni associations.</p>
    <a href="/about/" class="vision-link">About the BAA →</a>
  </div>
</section>

